Package scenario.integrita.database

Class HistoryTreeStore

java.lang.Object
scenario.integrita.database.HistoryTreeStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
Store
public class HistoryTreeStore extends Object implements Store
storage unit of the history tree. It contains methods to persist and update a database of history tree nodes.
